## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-319">零 (0) 值表示的扩展实体产生的字符数没有限制。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-319">A zero (0) value means no limits on the number of characters that result from expanding entities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-320">一个非零值指定的最大可以扩展实体产生的字符数。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-320">A non-zero value specifies the maximum number of characters that can result from expanding entities.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-321">如果读取器将尝试读取以便扩展的大小将超过此属性包含实体的文档<xref:System.Xml.XmlException>将引发。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-321">If the reader attempts to read a document that contains entities such that the expanded size will exceed this property, an <xref:System.Xml.XmlException> will be thrown.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-322">此属性，可以以缓解拒绝服务攻击，攻击者提交尝试超过内存限制通过扩展实体的 XML 文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-322">This property allows you to mitigate denial of service attacks where the attacker submits XML documents that attempt to exceed memory limits via expanding entities.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-323">通过限制从扩展实体产生的字符，可以检测攻击，并可靠地进行恢复。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-323">By limiting the characters that result from expanded entities, you can detect the attack and recover reliably.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-324">下面的代码设置此属性，然后尝试分析包含扩展的大小大于所设定的限制为的实体的文档。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-324">The following code sets this property, and then attempts to parse a document that contains an entity that expands to a size greater than the set limit.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="6d2df-325">在实际方案中，你将设置此限制为一个足够大，尚未处理有效的文档的值足够小，以限制从恶意文档的威胁。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="6d2df-325">In a real world scenario, you would set this limit to a value large enough to handle valid documents, yet small enough to limit the threat from malicious documents.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
string markup =  
@"<!DOCTYPE Root [  
  <!ENTITY anEntity ""Expands to more than 30 characters"">  
  <!ELEMENT Root (#PCDATA)>  
]>  
<Root>Content &anEntity;</Root>";  
  
XmlReaderSettings settings = new XmlReaderSettings();  
settings.DtdProcessing = DtdProcessing.Parse;  
settings.ValidationType = ValidationType.DTD;  
settings.MaxCharactersFromEntities = 30;  
  
try  
{  
    XmlReader reader = XmlReader.Create(new StringReader(markup), settings);  
    while (reader.Read()) { }  
}  
catch (XmlException ex)  
{  
    Console.WriteLine(ex.Message);  
}  
```  
  
